{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/use-the-every-method-to-check-that-every-element-in-an-array-meets-a-criteria","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"functional-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi putanju za svaki pregledati da li svaki element u nizu podataka zadovoljava kriterijume","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija <code>every</code> radi sa nizovima podataka da bi proverila da li svaki element prolazi određeni test. Vraća vrednost tačno ili netačno - <code>true</code> ako sve vrednosti zadovoljavaju kriterijume, <code>false</code> inače.</p>\n<p>Na primer, sledeći kod proverio bi da li je svaki element u redovima podataka <code>numbers</code> manji od 10:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const numbers = [1, 5, 8, 0, 10, 11];\r\n\r\nnumbers.every(function(currentValue) {\r\n  return currentValue &#x3C; 10;\r\n});\n</code></pre>\n<p>Putanja za <code>every</code> bi koristila <code>false</code> ovde.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7dab367417b2b2512b6e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi putanju <code>every</code> unutar funkcije <code>checkPositive</code> da proveri da li je svaki element u <code>arr</code> pozitivan. Funkcija bi trebalo da vrati vrednost tačno ili netačno.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301312,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/use-the-every-method-to-check-that-every-element-in-an-array-meets-a-criteria"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function checkPositive(arr) {\r\n  // Only change code below this line\r\n\r\n\r\n  // Only change code above this line\r\n}\r\n\r\ncheckPositive([1, 2, 3, -4, 5]);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoj kod bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>every</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/\\.every/g));"},{"text":"<p><code>checkPositive([1, 2, 3, -4, 5])</code> treba da vrati <code>false</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFalse(checkPositive([1, 2, 3, -4, 5]));"},{"text":"<p><code>checkPositive([1, 2, 3, 4, 5])</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>true</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(checkPositive([1, 2, 3, 4, 5]));"},{"text":"<p><code>checkPositive([1, -2, 3, -4, 5])</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>false</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFalse(checkPositive([1, -2, 3, -4, 5]));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#functional-programming","dashedName":"use-the-every-method-to-check-that-every-element-in-an-array-meets-a-criteria","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"functional-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/use-the-some-method-to-check-that-any-elements-in-an-array-meet-a-criteria","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/functional-programming/apply-functional-programming-to-convert-strings-to-url-slugs","id":"587d7dab367417b2b2512b6e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"const add = x => y => z => x + y + z","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javasc